Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system in the town of Aurora as the "Specialist Dale Sadowski Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Aurora as the "Specialist Dale Sadowski Memorial Bridge".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system in the town of Aurora as the "Specialist Dale Sadowski Memorial Bridge"
